title: LF Ranked friends, DUO or Team (Bronze - Silver)
body:
Hey, im a 21 YO male from england but i moved to melbourne recently, and after a 1 year break im looking to get back into LOL. 
I was Silver 2 last season i believe but im just looking for people to Duo with, make a ranked team or just chat  :)
am online most days, add my in game
cheers
TheRock

replies.body: Hi there, i am currently looking to make a ranked team and was wondering if you would be interested, i have sent you a friend request on league and would love to hear back from you.
